<h2 id="capo-4th-fret-to-play-with-willie">Capo 4th fret to play with Willie</h2>

<p>On this page, Iâ€™m teaching this song using chords in the key of C (which are easier to play than the key of E, which is what Willie uses). Add a capo on the 4th fret, using chords in C, to play with Willie. Otherwise, a capo isnâ€™t needed.</p>

