<h2 id="strumming-pattern">Strumming pattern</h2>

<p>To keep things simple, I recommend all downstrums (4 per measure) with accents on the 2 and 4 counts. See my video lesson for some context here.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>1 + 2 + 3 + 4 +
D   D   D   D
    &gt;       &gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>From there, you could add some upstrums within this pattern â€“ specifically in the final half.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>1 + 2 + 3 + 4 +
D   D   D U D U
    &gt;       &gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

